body:
@javelinjs what are the next steps here and do you need any help?

Now that mxnet is a apache incubator project I do think we need to change the package name prefix from `ml.dmlc` to `org.apache`. That is what all other apache projects have done.
Also, going forward I think we should automate the "publish artifacts to maven central" step that executes whenever a new release is cut. Lets talk about how to get there.
